Important Points
-----------------
  👉 A class is a blueprint.
  👉 A class is not an object.
  👉 Objects are created from classes.
  👉 A class can contain fields, methods, and constructors.
  👉 One class can create many objects.
  👉 Class names follow PascalCase.

